## 2. What Is Done

### ✅ Authentication & Authorization
- [x] OTP Send via `/auth/otp/send` with Fastify JSON Schema validation
- [x] OTP Verify via `/auth/otp/verify` with bcrypt hash comparison
- [x] OTP stored in PostgreSQL `OtpVerification` table (not Redis)
- [x] Digital lockout mechanism: `isLockedOut` + `lockoutUntil` on [User](file:///d:/SUVIDHA/services/auth/src/services/session.service.ts#87-107) model
- [x] JWT signing with HS256 (citizen: 30min, admin: 8hr expiry)
- [x] JWT refresh endpoint via `/auth/refresh`
- [x] Session model in DB with `jwtId`, `deviceId`, `ipAddress`, `expiresAt`
- [x] Admin session revocation endpoint: `DELETE /auth/admin/sessions/:userId`
- [x] Gateway JWT validation middleware ([validateJWT.ts](file:///d:/SUVIDHA/gateway/src/middleware/validateJWT.ts))
- [x] Gateway RBAC enforcement middleware ([rbacEnforcer.ts](file:///d:/SUVIDHA/gateway/src/middleware/rbacEnforcer.ts))
- [x] Admin UI strict role checking in Zustand store (rejects CITIZEN tokens)
- [x] MeriPehchaan SSO login page (UI only — callback not wired to real SSO)
- [x] Demo bypass login for both Kiosk and Admin UIs

### ✅ API Gateway
- [x] Express gateway with 11 middleware layers in correct order
- [x] Proxy to all 13 microservices via `proxyToService()`
- [x] Helmet security headers
- [x] CORS with configurable origin whitelist
- [x] Rate limiting (default + per-route OTP limiters)
- [x] JWT validation with public route bypass
- [x] RBAC enforcer with role-to-route mapping
- [x] Audit logger middleware
- [x] Structured JSON request logging with `traceId` injection

### ✅ Kiosk UI (Frontend)
- [x] Language selection page (en, hi, mr, ta, bn)
- [x] Mobile number entry with numeric keypad
- [x] OTP entry with 6-digit input, countdown timer, resend logic
- [x] OTP lockout UI handling (`AUTH_OTP_LOCKED`)
- [x] Home page with service cards
- [x] Bill detail page with consumer ID lookup
- [x] Payment mode selection (UPI/Card/NetBanking)
- [x] UPI payment page with QR code
- [x] Payment success with receipt download
- [x] Complaint form with category selection
- [x] Complaint tracking by reference number
- [x] Service request form (new connection, modification, etc.)
- [x] Advisory display page
- [x] QR continue (mobile handoff)
- [x] Session timeout modal with countdown
- [x] Advisory bar and emergency broadcast modal
- [x] Axios interceptor for 401 auto-refresh
- [x] Voice input component (Bhashini ASR stub)
- [x] Accessibility panel

### ✅ Admin UI (Frontend)
- [x] Login page with MeriPehchaan SSO redirect
- [x] SSO callback handler
- [x] Dashboard with summary cards
- [x] Complaint list with filters
- [x] Complaint detail with status update
- [x] Advisory list and editor
- [x] Analytics reports page
- [x] Kiosk health monitoring page
- [x] Kiosk management settings
- [x] Service config settings
- [x] User management page
- [x] Protected routes with RequireAuth guard

### ✅ Infrastructure
- [x] Docker Compose with all 18 containers
- [x] PostgreSQL 15 with health checks
- [x] Redis 7 with health checks
- [x] Prisma schema with 20+ models and all enums
- [x] Multi-stage Docker builds for all services
- [x] Environment variable configuration (.env with 126 lines)
- [x] GitLab CI pipeline configuration

### ✅ Document Service
- [x] PDF receipt generation (Python + ReportLab)
- [x] Receipt download endpoint
- [x] Public receipt verification via HMAC-SHA256
- [x] Thermal printer support (ESC/POS)

