## 3. Known Bugs & Issues

### 🔴 Critical

| # | Issue | Service | Details |
|---|-------|---------|---------|
| 1 | **Notification service HTTP binding** | notification | Was using `httpServer.listen()` bypassing Fastify router — **FIXED** but needs Docker rebuild verification |
| 2 | **CORS not configured for Vite dev** | gateway | `CORS_ORIGINS` in [.env](file:///d:/SUVIDHA/.env) file still only has `:80,:8080` — docker-compose was fixed but [.env](file:///d:/SUVIDHA/.env) is stale |
| 3 | **Advisory store undefined crash** | kiosk-ui | `advisories.filter()` on undefined — **FIXED** with [(advisories \|\| [])](file:///d:/SUVIDHA/admin-ui/src/lib/utils.ts#4-7) |
| 4 | **OTP payload missing kioskId/ulbId** | kiosk-ui | Frontend was sending only `{mobile}` — **FIXED** by adding `kioskId` and `ulbId` from env |
| 5 | **Database tables not created** | all | `prisma migrate deploy` has never been run against PostgreSQL — tables likely don't exist |
| 6 | **No seed data** | all | No ULBs, wards, kiosks, complaint categories, or config entries exist in DB |

### 🟡 Medium

| # | Issue | Service | Details |
|---|-------|---------|---------|
| 7 | `VITE_KIOSK_ID` is a string `"KIOSK-DEV-001"` but schema expects UUID | kiosk-ui | Will cause FK validation errors when creating sessions |
| 8 | MeriPehchaan SSO callback is **UI-only** — no backend token exchange | auth | Admin login will fail in non-demo mode |
| 9 | SMS Provider is `MOCK` — OTPs are only logged to console | auth | No actual SMS delivery in dev or staging |
| 10 | `react-router-dom` v6 deprecation warnings | kiosk-ui | Should migrate to v7 or suppress warnings |
| 11 | Tailwind `@import` order error in kiosk-ui CSS | kiosk-ui | `@import must precede all other statements` |
| 12 | `npm audit` vulnerabilities not addressed | all | Multiple packages have known vulnerabilities |

### 🟢 Low

| # | Issue | Details |
|---|-------|---------|
| 13 | Docker `version` attribute is obsolete | Remove `version: '3.9'` from docker-compose.yml |
| 14 | Admin UI build warning: chunk > 500kB | Need code splitting / manual chunks |
| 15 | Redis eviction policy warning in notification service | Should be `noeviction` for BullMQ |

