## 6. Indian DPI Integrations

These are the Government Digital Public Infrastructure (DPI) platforms SUVIDHA must integrate with for production deployment:

| DPI Platform | Purpose | Status | What You Need |
|---|---|---|---|
| **BBPS (NPCI)** | Bill fetch & payment | 🔴 Mock only | BBPS Agent ID, Agent Secret, mTLS certs |
| **MeriPehchaan** | Admin SSO | 🔴 UI only | OAuth2 client_id, client_secret, sandbox |
| **DigiLocker** | Document verification | 🔴 Not started | NIC client_id, client_secret |
| **Bhashini** | Speech-to-text | 🔴 Mock only | API key, pipeline URL, user ID |
| **Mappls/MapmyIndia** | Geolocation | 🔴 Mock only | API key with geocoding access |
| **UPI (NPCI)** | Payment | 🔴 Mock only | Merchant VPA, gateway integration |
| **MSG91 / CDAC** | SMS delivery | 🔴 Mock only | Auth key, DLT template IDs |
| **MeghRaj Cloud** | Object storage | 🔴 Not started | S3-compatible credentials |
| **Aadhaar (UIDAI)** | eKYC (optional) | 🔴 Not started | AUA/KUA license, ASA agreement |

